post.description:
Configure YouTube Video Posts scraping parameters with Novada **Scraper API**. Supports batch collection via video URL, search filters, tags, podcast URL, keywords, and explore pages — retrieving video title, view count, likes, comments, channel subscribers, duration, upload date, transcript, and more. Exports in JSON/CSV/XLSX format.

**scraper_params** (JSON array) item schema:
```json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "url": {
      "type": "string"
    }
  },
  "example": {
    "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HAwTwmzgNc4"
  }
}
```
